{"tid":2371422,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"689: 如果焚燒靖國神社事件發生在香港，泛民會怎樣說？","createTime":"2021-01-19T00:23:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T15:02:09.000Z","uid":230530,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"31a8b188e968fd572e21b81d50f07795a9570420","tid":2371422,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T00:23:07.000Z","msg":"如果發生在香港，泛民會怎麼説？香港法院的量刑和日本的孰輕孰重？<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果即時新聞》報道，郭紹傑、嚴敏華上訴遭駁回。<br />\n<br />\n郭嚴二人18年在日本靖國神社外焚燒道具神主牌示威，遭控告擅闖建築物罪並判緩刑，兩人上訴，日本最高法院已駁回上訴裁決，維持原判，即是郭紹傑有期徒刑8個月、緩刑3年；嚴敏華有期徒刑6個月、緩刑3年。"},{"pid":"2edc2abea5e1c11134c67609dfb12ef9e0315193","tid":2371422,"uid":230530,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T00:23:27.000Z","msg":"原來689 有裝蘋果😍😍"},{"pid":"1a55e688ed70b711a0e1cc7fd468405d2eb85ccd","tid":2371422,"uid":3481,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T00:28:50.000Z","msg":"飯民咩回應冇人知，呢個年代根本冇人care咩拜唔拜靖國神社<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50d46d4b5d6e250fb0147cbc3f4d8fe2e71bb9f","tid":2371422,"uid":51271,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T00:30:39.000Z","msg":"如果你死去，我知道香檳會斷市"},{"pid":"ad1d7b88e6d992471bee1d4483532625257d923a","tid":2371422,"uid":18477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T00:31:35.000Z","msg":"喺香港嘅話高尚情操當庭釋放添啦<br />\n只要你係blue objects"},{"pid":"1e734ae1a6b324d7837e317e30f3c8786bae2245","tid":2371422,"uid":151074,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T00:35:21.000Z","msg":"下放火喎，香港就告暴動坐五年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲問<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9916c05b4d38e672af9b6775eb85372496004cc5","tid":2371422,"uid":11291,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T00:36:03.000Z","msg":"如果天